entries.journal_entry_description: Stren Colo's bounty office is offering 12,000 credits on the head of the Sabacc cheater Jessk.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Tien has indicated that Jessk has traveled back to Mos Eisley and wants you to pursue him there.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Some of Lady Valarian's henchmen have decided that you look like easy prey.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: You have failed the Jessk Bounty
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Shortly after your battle with the Valarians, you overhear talk of a gambler that was cheated in the Cantina.  Maybe this is the work of Jessk.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: You have spotted the card cheater Jessk in his travels away from Mos Eisley.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Now that you have directions for Jessk, track him and end his cheating ways.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Visit Stren at the bounty office in Kachirho to collect your reward.
